#: ../../language/error_codes/E3024.md:1
msgid "E3024"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3024.md:3
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Legacy constructor functions declared inside a `struct` must have name "
"`new`."
msgstr "`struct` 的构造函数必须命名为 `new`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3024.md:5
msgid ""
"This error happens when a constructor function declared inside a `struct`"
" is not named `new`. MoonBit treats `new` as the constructor entry point "
"for the struct."
msgstr "当在 `struct` 内声明的构造函数没有命名为 `new` 时，会发生此错误。MoonBit 将 `new` 视为该结构体的构造入口。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3024.md:9
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3024.md:11
msgid ""
"pub struct S {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"  fn constr(x : Int) -> S\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"fn S::constr(x : Int) -> S {\n"
"  { x, }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3024.md:15
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3024.md:17
msgid "Define the constructor with the current top-level `Type::Type` form:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3024.md:19
msgid ""
"pub struct S {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"fn S::S(x : Int) -> S {\n"
"  { x, }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"pub fn make(x : Int) -> S {\n"
"  S(x)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#~ msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `struct_constr_invalid_name`."
#~ msgstr ""

